            <div corresp="#c3638f2">
                <head>Basel, Switzerland</head>
                <p>H. Merle Cochran directed by telegram dated Aug. 31, 1932, to report to Dept. of
                    State for Consultation; detailed to Geneva for temp. duty as Adviser to the Am.
                    Experts on the Monetary &amp; Economic Conference Oct. 15, 1932.</p>
                <p>Alfred T. Burri detailed to Dept. of State, temp., Nov. 15, 1933; redetailed to
                    Dept. of State, temp., Dec. 22, 1933.</p>
